any mirti for Instance a a railway company or fur a joint stock company of any kind to contribute from Ita funds to the campaign chest of political parties The thing in not unknown there wa case about a year ago In which the directors of on of the great railway companies wore found to have sub fcrlbcl to the moderate party In the Londa county council elections Hut on th whole the practice is frowned upon both by public opinion and by the general sense of the commercial community Nor does the political ne cessity for It exist in England Three reasons I believe writes Sydney Brooks In Harpers Weekly are usu ally given to explain the Intimacy of the allance between corporations and politics In the United States The first is that In an expanding half de veloped country the number of good"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2020-09-15T12:05:42.484Z", "group": ["ndnp/mohi", "state-historical-society-of-missouri-columbia-mo-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn90061663/1908-05-07/ed-1/?sp=4", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:mohi:batch_mohi_jerome_ver01:data:sn90061663:00280779684:1908050701:0982/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=408&w=281", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:mohi:batch_mohi_jerome_ver01:data:sn90061663:00280779684:1908050701:0982/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=817&w=563", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/mohi/batch_mohi_jerome_ver01/data/sn90061663/00280779684/1908050701/0982.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "location": ["missouri", "united states", "rich hill", "bates county", "bates"], "location_city": ["rich hill"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["bates"], "location_state": ["missouri"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/pdf", "text/xml", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "application/json", "text/plain"], "number": ["9", "0", "8", "0000000004", "sn90061663",